column5: We woke up to high winds 37 k and gusts to 57km so we waited till there was a bit of light before we headed out we tried to stay on our fish from yesterday but could not do to the wind gusts. We kept trolling and after 4 hours we get our first hit, a jumbo perch. Another hour goes buy and we start to think we may have that smell of walleye skunk but a rod goes off once again and its a big walleye but we loose it. The smell of skunk starts to come back. 15 min later its fish on for 2.5 hours We went 16 for 20 and I matched my PB with a 13 and a half pound monster with a 12.5 and a few nine and tens also today most of the smaller boats hand a hard time staying on the fish do to the wild winds. Heard Paul had a big pike to the net..there is a story going around that women on a boat is bad luck..but that is another story and another and another
You run out of "file" pictures yet? lol
I see UFC 134 all over this.      Man, you guys are on them this weekend.GJ.
That diver must be damn tired today.. out in that crap..
Nice to see you guys still found the fish despite the weather. Another banner day.
Awesome Terry You guys are on fire     Nice gold Leechman

Loyd sure is on the fish. Aren't you lucky Terry, we cleared out the no fish spots. Congrats on the PB  . You guys got my buddy's thinking of going down again next week.   I guess I don't put the boat away yet.
Nice Eyes, it pays to stick it out some times, the Fish Gods are good to you guys Richard
come on.. where's day three.. iced up boat.. many fish.. home early.. DANG.. I could have been home and back to TO you guys packed up so early!!
I had to eat clean up  get my overly swelled with pride head(details later) , in the door
No Wayne,his wife told him or else.

What a great crew I had this year. Made my job very easy to stay on fish and have a very relaxing weekend.  Wayne every day we put a rod out for you and look forward to having you back on the boat next year.  Not having you and Dano out with me this year was a very strange feeling for me but we will have next year.  Get well Dano A.K.A BUBBLE BOY   LOL and good Luck Wayne with your daughter.
